<h1>Messaging Example</h1>

<p>
    This example shows how to send asynchronously messages.<br/>
    The message is sent from <code>com.tchepannou.rails.sample.action.ExampleActionController.jmsSubmit()</code>,<br/>
    The message is received by <code>com.tchepannou.rails.sample.action.ExampleActionController.say()</code>
</p>
<form method="post" action="$request.contextPath/example/jmsSubmit">
    <table>
        <tr>
            <td>Type a Message</td>
            <td><input name="msg" value="$!{msg}"/></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="2">
                <input type="submit" />
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</form>

<p>Back to <a href="$request.contextPath/home">home</a></p>
